1. *Čuli* smo kako se iz daljine čuje zvuk motora. (We heard how the sound of the engine is heard from afar.)

2. Oni su čuli da je ona dobro. (They heard that she was well.)

3. *Čuti* ću te kroz zid. (I will hear you through the wall.)

4. Ono što sam čuo nije bilo dobro. (What I heard was not good.)

5. Ona je *čula* kako se veselje širi. (She heard how the joy is spreading.)